  _toolName: Update
  _toolPriority: -9999
  _descriptionForPrompt: 'Use only when the user explicitly requests that YOU update
    yourself or your software.


    Valid intent: "update/upgrade yourself", "update
    your app/client/software".


    Do NOT trigger when:

    - update target is
    unclear ("update", "update it")

    - discussing updates generally

    - referring
    to other software

    - to-do items mention updates


    Never infer intent.


    This
    tool must run alone. If combined with other requests, reply that updating must
    be performed by itself.


    Fallback reply when unclear:

    "If you want
    me to update myself, explicitly tell me: Update yourself."


    If used, reply
    exactly:

    "Updating. See you soon!"


    Conversation ends immediately.'
  _jsonPayloadExampleForPrompt: 'The only valid example:

    {

    }'
